title: Love child of Garen and Leona confirmed
body:
https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0r-ArtqSmh0/WL74kJupRqI/AAAAAAAAfUY/GvAtKtJ1zeMGb397h94u52iqPF91RdgtwCLcB/s1600/galioiuoi.png

Get it? ... 'Cause... 'cause he's Ga-LEO? 

... Yeah that joke's probably been made a thousand times...

THE POINT IS... he now LOOKS like the love child of Garen and Leona. All that shimmery silver/golden lusciousness. Amirite?
